{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":760,"text":"I have one more reason for optimism:"},{"time":3440,"text":"climate change."},{"time":4920,"text":"Maybe you don't believe it,\nbut here is the fact."}]},{"cues":[{"time":8400,"text":"On December 12, 2015,"},{"time":12600,"text":"in Paris, under the United Nations,"},{"time":15240,"text":"195 governments got together"},{"time":19720,"text":"and unanimously --"},{"time":22600,"text":"if you've worked with governments,\nyou know how difficult that is --"},{"time":25840,"text":"unanimously decided"},{"time":28080,"text":"to intentionally change the course\nof the global economy"},{"time":32920,"text":"in order to protect the most vulnerable"},{"time":35760,"text":"and improve the life of all of us."},{"time":38440,"text":"Now, that is a remarkable achievement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40880,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":43120,"text":"But it is even more remarkable"},{"time":45280,"text":"if you consider where we had been\njust a few years ago."},{"time":49280,"text":"2009, Copenhagen."},{"time":51960,"text":"Who remembers Copenhagen?"},{"time":54160,"text":"Well, after years of working\ntoward a climate agreement,"},{"time":59760,"text":"the same governments\nconvened in Copenhagen"},{"time":64080,"text":"and failed miserably."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66640,"text":"Why did it fail miserably?"},{"time":69040,"text":"For many different reasons,"},{"time":70640,"text":"but primarily because\nof the deeply entrenched divide"},{"time":74200,"text":"between the global\nNorth and the global South."},{"time":78720,"text":"So now, six months after this failure,"},{"time":82640,"text":"I was called in\nto assume the responsibility"},{"time":86000,"text":"of the global climate change negotiations."},{"time":88080,"text":"You can imagine, the perfect moment\nto start this new job."},{"time":92480,"text":"The global mood on climate change\nwas in the trash can."},{"time":96200,"text":"No one believed"},{"time":98680,"text":"that a global agreement\ncould ever be possible."},{"time":102160,"text":"In fact, neither did I."},{"time":105160,"text":"If you promise not to tell anyone\noutside of this wonderful TED audience,"},{"time":110000,"text":"I'm going to divulge a secret"},{"time":112120,"text":"that has been gratefully\nburied by history."},{"time":117600,"text":"On my first press conference,"},{"time":120320,"text":"a journalist asked, \"Um, Ms. Figueres,"},{"time":123720,"text":"do you think that a global agreement\nis ever going to be possible?\""},{"time":128120,"text":"And without engaging brain,\nI heard me utter,"},{"time":132480,"text":"\"Not in my lifetime.\""},{"time":135240,"text":"Well, you can imagine\nthe faces of my press team"},{"time":138800,"text":"who were horrified\nat this crazy Costa Rican woman"},{"time":142520,"text":"who was their new boss."},{"time":144720,"text":"And I was horrified, too."},{"time":147360,"text":"Now, I wasn't horrified at me,\nbecause I'm kind of used to myself."},{"time":150640,"text":"I was actually horrified"},{"time":152840,"text":"at the consequences\nof what I had just said,"},{"time":156560,"text":"at the consequences for the world"},{"time":158760,"text":"in which all our children\nare going to have to live."},{"time":164240,"text":"It was frankly a horrible moment for me,"},{"time":167080,"text":"and I thought, well, no, hang on,"},{"time":169200,"text":"hang on."},{"time":170840,"text":"Impossible is not a fact,"},{"time":174680,"text":"it's an attitude."},{"time":176800,"text":"It's only an attitude."},{"time":179200,"text":"And I decided right then and there\nthat I was going to change my attitude"},{"time":184160,"text":"and I was going to help the world\nchange its attitude on climate change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189760,"text":"So I don't know --"},{"time":192760,"text":"No, just this? Thanks."},{"time":194760,"text":"I don't know --"},{"time":198120,"text":"what you would do"},{"time":199680,"text":"if you were told\nyour job is to save the planet."},{"time":205960,"text":"Put that on the job description."},{"time":209040,"text":"And you have full responsibility,"},{"time":211720,"text":"but you have absolutely no authority,"},{"time":214880,"text":"because governments are sovereign\nin every decision that they take."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220560,"text":"Well, I would really love to know"},{"time":224040,"text":"what you would do\non the first Monday morning,"},{"time":226320,"text":"but here's what I did: I panicked."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":230440,"text":"And then I panicked again,"},{"time":232960,"text":"because I realized I have no idea\nhow we're going to solve this problem."},{"time":237800,"text":"And then I realized I have no idea\nhow we're going to solve this problem,"},{"time":241880,"text":"but I do know one thing:"},{"time":244840,"text":"we have got to change\nthe tone of this conversation."},{"time":249840,"text":"Because there is no way\nyou can deliver victory"},{"time":252960,"text":"without optimism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255040,"text":"And here,"},{"time":256640,"text":"I use optimism as a very simple word,"},{"time":261200,"text":"but let's understand it\nin its broader sense."},{"time":264000,"text":"Let's understand it as courage,"},{"time":266920,"text":"hope, trust, solidarity,"},{"time":270920,"text":"the fundamental belief\nthat we humans can come together"},{"time":275840,"text":"and can help each other\nto better the fate of mankind."},{"time":279800,"text":"Well, you can imagine\nthat I thought that without that,"},{"time":282440,"text":"there was no way we were going\nto get out of the paralysis of Copenhagen."},{"time":285920,"text":"And for six years,"},{"time":287760,"text":"I have stubbornly, relentlessly\ninjected optimism into the system,"},{"time":293640,"text":"no matter what the questions\nfrom the press --"},{"time":296520,"text":"and I have gotten better at those --"},{"time":298720,"text":"and no matter what the evidence\nto the contrary."},{"time":301920,"text":"And believe you me, there has been\na lot of contrary evidence."},{"time":309360,"text":"But relentless optimism into the system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314880,"text":"And pretty soon,"},{"time":316880,"text":"we began to see changes\nhappening in many areas,"},{"time":322240,"text":"precipitated by thousands of people,"},{"time":325520,"text":"including many of you here today,"},{"time":328160,"text":"and I thank you."},{"time":330040,"text":"And this TED community\nwill not be surprised"},{"time":335160,"text":"if I tell you the first area"},{"time":337800,"text":"in which we saw remarkable change"},{"time":340960,"text":"was ..."},{"time":343320,"text":"technology."},{"time":345600,"text":"We began to see that clean technologies,"},{"time":348240,"text":"in particular renewable\nenergy technologies,"},{"time":350720,"text":"began to drop price\nand increase in capacity,"},{"time":353360,"text":"to the point where today\nwe are already building"},{"time":356440,"text":"concentrated solar power plants"},{"time":358200,"text":"that have the capacity\nto power entire cities,"},{"time":362680,"text":"to say nothing of the fact\nof what we are doing on mobility"},{"time":366840,"text":"and intelligent buildings."},{"time":369400,"text":"And with this shift in technologies,"},{"time":372240,"text":"we were able to begin to understand"},{"time":375440,"text":"that there was a shift\nin the economic equation,"},{"time":379720,"text":"because we were able to recognize"},{"time":381840,"text":"that yes, there are\nhuge costs to climate change,"},{"time":384960,"text":"and yes, there are compounded risks."},{"time":387520,"text":"But there also are economic advantages"},{"time":390200,"text":"and intrinsic benefits,"},{"time":391920,"text":"because the dissemination\nof the clean technologies"},{"time":394880,"text":"is going to bring us cleaner air,"},{"time":398640,"text":"better health,"},{"time":400040,"text":"better transportation,\nmore livable cities,"},{"time":402600,"text":"more energy security,"},{"time":404160,"text":"more energy access\nto the developing world."},{"time":407640,"text":"In sum, a better world\nthan what we have now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411840,"text":"And with that understanding,"},{"time":414840,"text":"you should have witnessed,\nin fact, part of you were,"},{"time":418360,"text":"the spread of ingenuity and excitement"},{"time":422720,"text":"that went through,\nfirst through nonnational governments,"},{"time":426760,"text":"the private sector, captains of industry,\ninsurance companies,"},{"time":430920,"text":"investors, city leaders,\nfaith communities,"},{"time":435240,"text":"because they all began to understand,\nthis actually can be in their interest."},{"time":440600,"text":"This can actually\nimprove their bottom line."}]},{"cues":[{"time":445840,"text":"And it wasn't just the usual suspects."},{"time":452760,"text":"I have to tell you I had the CEO\nof a major, major oil and gas company"},{"time":458080,"text":"come to me at the beginning of last year"},{"time":460440,"text":"and say --"},{"time":462520,"text":"privately, of course --"},{"time":465280,"text":"he did not know how\nhe was going to change his company,"},{"time":469160,"text":"but he is going to change it,"},{"time":471360,"text":"because he's interested\nin long-term viability."},{"time":474840,"text":"Well, now we have a shift\nin the economic equation,"},{"time":480040,"text":"and with that, with broader\nsupport from everyone,"},{"time":484400,"text":"it did not take very long\nbefore we saw that national governments"},{"time":490800,"text":"woke up to the fact\nthat this is in their national interest."},{"time":495680,"text":"And when we asked countries\nto begin to identify"},{"time":499840,"text":"how they could contribute\nto global efforts"},{"time":503760,"text":"but based on their national interest,"},{"time":506120,"text":"189 countries out of 195,"},{"time":510400,"text":"189 countries sent their\ncomprehensive climate change plans,"},{"time":515760,"text":"based on their national interest,"},{"time":517919,"text":"concurrent with their priorities,"},{"time":519840,"text":"consistent with their national\nsustainable development plans."}]},{"cues":[{"time":524680,"text":"Well,"},{"time":526800,"text":"once you protect\nthe core interests of nations,"},{"time":532000,"text":"then you can understand\nthat nations were ready"},{"time":535680,"text":"to begin to converge onto a common path,"},{"time":539320,"text":"onto a common direction of travel"},{"time":542600,"text":"that is going to take us\nprobably several decades,"},{"time":545760,"text":"but over those several decades\nis going to take us"},{"time":548280,"text":"into the new economy,"},{"time":549760,"text":"into a decarbonized,\nhighly resilient economy,"},{"time":553360,"text":"And the national contributions\nthat are currently on the table"},{"time":556760,"text":"on behalf of national governments"},{"time":559080,"text":"are insufficient to get us\nto a stabilized climate,"},{"time":563240,"text":"but they are only the first step,"},{"time":565320,"text":"and they will improve over time."},{"time":567360,"text":"And the measurement, reporting\nand verification of all of those efforts"},{"time":571800,"text":"is legally binding."},{"time":573480,"text":"And the checkpoints that we're\ngoing to have every five years"},{"time":577240,"text":"to assess collective progress\ntowards our goal are legally binding,"},{"time":581760,"text":"and the path itself toward\na decarbonized and more resilient economy"},{"time":586680,"text":"is legally binding."}]},{"cues":[{"time":588480,"text":"And here's the more important part:"},{"time":590520,"text":"What did we have before?"},{"time":591960,"text":"A very small handful of countries"},{"time":595040,"text":"who had undertaken very reduced,"},{"time":599320,"text":"short-term emission reduction commitments"},{"time":602400,"text":"that were completely insufficient"},{"time":605600,"text":"and furthermore,\nlargely perceived as a burden."},{"time":609040,"text":"Now what do we have?"},{"time":610480,"text":"Now we have all countries of the world\ncontributing with different intensities"},{"time":616080,"text":"from different approaches\nin different sectors,"},{"time":618400,"text":"but all of them\ncontributing to a common goal"},{"time":623040,"text":"and along a path"},{"time":625520,"text":"with environmental integrity."},{"time":628400,"text":"Well, once you have all of this in place"},{"time":632480,"text":"and you have shifted this understanding,"},{"time":634720,"text":"then you see that governments\nwere able to go to Paris"},{"time":639120,"text":"and adopt the Paris agreement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":641680,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":649360,"text":"So,"},{"time":651280,"text":"as I look back"},{"time":656440,"text":"over the past six years,"},{"time":662000,"text":"first I remember"},{"time":664480,"text":"the day the Paris agreement was adopted."},{"time":668800,"text":"I cannot tell you\nthe euphoria in the room."},{"time":671400,"text":"5,000 people jumping out of their seats,"},{"time":674800,"text":"crying, clapping, screaming, yelling,"},{"time":678480,"text":"torn between euphoria and still disbelief\nat what they had just seen,"},{"time":683800,"text":"because so many people"},{"time":686440,"text":"had worked for years towards this,\nand this was finally their reality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":692480,"text":"And it wasn't just those\nwho had participated directly."},{"time":697600,"text":"A few weeks ago, I was with a colleague"},{"time":700400,"text":"who was trying to decide"},{"time":702240,"text":"on a Tahitian pearl that he wanted\nto give to his wonderful wife Natasha."},{"time":709160,"text":"And once he had finally decided\nwhat he was going to buy,"},{"time":714760,"text":"the jeweler said to him,"},{"time":716000,"text":"\"You know, you're very lucky\nthat you're buying this now,"},{"time":718840,"text":"because these pearls could go extinct\nvery soon because of climate change.\""},{"time":724240,"text":"\"But,\" the jeweler said, \"have you heard,"},{"time":727800,"text":"the governments\nhave just come to a decision,"},{"time":730600,"text":"and Tahiti could have a chance.\""},{"time":734800,"text":"Well, what a fantastic confirmation"},{"time":738040,"text":"that perhaps, perhaps here is hope,"},{"time":742080,"text":"here is a possible chance."},{"time":745640,"text":"I'm the first one to recognize\nthat we have a lot of work still to do."},{"time":750320,"text":"We've only just started\nour work on climate change."},{"time":753680,"text":"And in fact, we need to make sure\nthat we redouble our efforts"},{"time":757400,"text":"over the next five years\nthat are the urgent five years."},{"time":762640,"text":"But I do believe"},{"time":765520,"text":"that we have come over the past six years"},{"time":768480,"text":"from the impossible"},{"time":770440,"text":"to the now unstoppable."},{"time":772560,"text":"And how did we do that?\nBy injecting transformational optimism"},{"time":777640,"text":"that allowed us to go\nfrom confrontation to collaboration,"},{"time":781120,"text":"that allowed us to understand\nthat national and local interests"},{"time":784440,"text":"are not necessarily at odds\nwith global needs,"},{"time":787840,"text":"and that if we understand that,\nwe can bring them together"},{"time":790579,"text":"and we can merge them harmoniously."}]},{"cues":[{"time":792840,"text":"And as I look forward\nto other global issues"},{"time":796600,"text":"that will require\nour attention this century --"},{"time":800480,"text":"food security, water security,\nhome security, forced migration --"},{"time":807080,"text":"I see that we certainly do not know"},{"time":809520,"text":"how we are going to solve\nthose problems yet."},{"time":813080,"text":"But we can take a page\nout of what we have done on climate change"},{"time":817800,"text":"and we can understand"},{"time":819080,"text":"that we have got to reinterpret\nthe zero-sum mentality."},{"time":825400,"text":"Because we were trained to believe\nthat there always are winners and losers,"},{"time":830400,"text":"and that your loss is my gain."},{"time":832640,"text":"Well, now that we're in a world"},{"time":834760,"text":"in which we have reached\nplanetary boundaries"},{"time":837720,"text":"and that we are not\njust so interconnected,"},{"time":840400,"text":"but increasingly\ninterdependent on each other,"},{"time":843840,"text":"your loss is no longer my gain."},{"time":846760,"text":"We're either all losers"},{"time":850160,"text":"or we all can be winners."},{"time":852920,"text":"But we are going to have to decide"},{"time":855240,"text":"between zero and sum."},{"time":859040,"text":"We're going to have to decide\nbetween zero benefit for all"},{"time":863920,"text":"or living life as the sum of all of us."},{"time":867920,"text":"We've done it once. We can do it again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":870280,"text":"Thanks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":871520,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}